    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A type of Dutch flat-bottomed, half decked, sloop-rigged fishing vessel, mainly found in the southern part of the former Zuiderzee. It is a commonly fished with trawls and silage nets.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
